Hymn.Arabic: " لك هي السموات، ولك هي الأرض أيضًا، أنت أسست المسكونة وكمالها،
Hymn.English: 11 The heavens are Yours, the earth also is Yours; The world and all its fullness, You have founded them.
12 The north and the south, You have created them.
13 Strong is Your hand, and high is Your right hand.     Alleluia
